ch.\" However, the proposition does not exclude collateral tokens or require a governance token, airdrop, or TGE. The Help Center (PX-6) confirms no airdrop/TGE was announced while simultaneously calling pUSD Polymarket's \"official collateral token\" — which aligns with plaintiff's position, not the defense's added limitation.\n\nUnder preponderance, the record proves Polymarket launched an official fungible ERC-20 token (pUSD) before the deadline through official channels.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_0c65302b45194ff888f75f90","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The admitted record proves by preponderance that Polymarket launched pUSD, an official fungible ERC-20"},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"The admitted record proves by preponderance that Polymarket launched pUSD, an official fungible ERC-20","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"qwen/qwen3.5-plus-02-15","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782822962624,"responseId":"gen-1782822962-iqYw289OeY5lnb8mBo6j","responseModel":"qwen/qwen3.5-plus-20260216"}}
